---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro'
---

<Base
  title="Bettingbot — Aryan Sidbatte"
  description="Case study: Discord betting bot with horse races, parimutuel wagering, and AWS ECS Fargate deployment via Terraform and GitHub Actions."
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-24">

    <!-- Back link -->
    <a href="/" data-cursor-scale class="inline-block text-sm text-muted hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity mb-10">
      ← Back
    </a>

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary tracking-tight mb-3">Bettingbot</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-secondary mb-5">
        Discord betting bot with horse races, parimutuel wagering, and AWS deployment.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
        {['Python', 'discord.py', 'PostgreSQL', 'Docker', 'ECS Fargate', 'Terraform', 'GitHub Actions'].map(tag => (
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-muted border border-border bg-page px-2 py-1 rounded">
            {tag}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/aryansidbatte/bettingbot"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        data-cursor-scale
        class="text-sm text-muted hover:underline underline-offset-2 transition-all"
      >
        View on GitHub ↗
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Overview</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-[1.7]">
        Built for my Discord server. Members earn virtual points and spend them on custom
        multi-outcome bets or simulated horse races. Started on a Raspberry Pi running SQLite,
        then migrated to AWS ECS Fargate with RDS Postgres — I wanted to see what real production
        infrastructure actually looked like. Push to main, tests run, image builds, ECS updates.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- My role -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-3">My role</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-[1.7]">
        Solo. I wrote all the code, designed the database schema, built the Terraform
        infrastructure, and set up the CI/CD pipeline.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Key systems -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-6">Key systems</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-2">Horse races</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-[1.7]">
            4–6 randomly selected horses, 60-second betting window. Before the race starts,
            a Monte Carlo simulation runs 10,000 iterations to estimate win probabilities.
            The race is a single Discord message edited 9 times for animated progress.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-2">Custom bets</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-[1.7]">
            Any member can create a multi-outcome bet, others wager points, and the creator
            resolves it. Payouts split from the pool proportionally.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-2">Voice channel rewards</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-[1.7]">
            Members earn 1 carat per hour in voice chat. A background loop ticks every minute
            and writes to the database so state survives restarts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-2">AWS deployment</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-[1.7]">
            Container runs on ECS Fargate at 0.25 vCPU / 512 MB. Credentials live in Secrets
            Manager, injected at startup. CloudWatch captures structured JSON logs and fires
            a crash alert via SNS.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Architecture diagram -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-6">Architecture</h2>
      <img
        src="/images/bettingbot-architecture.svg"
        alt="Bettingbot AWS architecture diagram"
        loading="lazy"
        class="rounded-lg border border-border w-full bg-surface p-4"
      />
    </section>

    <!-- Repo CTA -->
    <a
      href="https://github.com/aryansidbatte/bettingbot"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      data-cursor-label="Visit"
      class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 text-sm text-secondary border border-border bg-surface hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity rounded-md"
    >
      View the repo on GitHub ↗
    </a>

  </main>
</Base>
